CD rom多<br />\n另外發現自己真係好愛香港"},{"pid":"13c6cdf1fb240b4ab632f09a2d3b9072bc9f2404","tid":1222320,"uid":24615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"發夢（真係訓著果隻發夢）捉撚左d差佬 用好殘忍既方式折磨死佢地<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日都有發 日日唔同玩法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都好擔心已經有心理病"},{"pid":"f6cdf6123e55886d3e2200d84ed218efc677bb62","tid":1222320,"uid":45370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"會同自己講 <br />\n喊乜野 應該留番贏左感動先喊"},{"pid":"ff8af4686c4fb111153e6c4d20fc75590194cc5b","tid":1222320,"uid":124017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1c3d15f5c3da43617203a3287d0555ed092281","tid":1222320,"uid":124017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:00:52.000Z","msg":"我有朋友本身有Ptsd 經過今次都病發<br />\n抗爭成功後 我哋再組織心理輔導小隊<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲們 可以下載 330 app 正念可以舒緩同放鬆身心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲們 如已出現情緒問題（失眠、失焦）等等<br />\n可以嘗試以下的方法 有助舒緩你們的情緒<br />\n<br />\n<strong>音樂治療（Music therapy）</strong><br />\n一首名為〈Weightless〉的音樂，減壓效果最佳，可令參與者的焦慮整體減少65%，平常生理休息率（usual physiological resting rates）可減低35%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYnA9wWFHLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqYnA9wWFHLI&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=b221451d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYnA9wWFHLI</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>靜觀（Mindfulness）</strong><br />\n新生精神康復會的newlife 330計劃，是為了配合推廣身心靈健康活動，推出的「newlife‧330」是少數免費的中文手機app之一。<br />\nGoogle Play：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.newlife330&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.newlife330%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c0383b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.newlife330&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\nApp Store：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/newlife-330/id1047078127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fnewlife-330%2Fid1047078127&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=91bf384f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/newlife-330/id1047078127</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>催眠治療（Hypnotherapy）</strong><br />\nVoid 利用手機應用程式作為媒介，把催眠治療、正念、冥想帶來的價值以簡單而有效的方式傳遞予更多人。<br />\nGoogle Play：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.appvoid.avoid&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dnet.appvoid.avoid%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=541a8df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.appvoid.avoid&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\nApp Store：<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/void-e4-b8-ad-e6-96-87-e6-94-be-e7-a9-ba-e5-86-a5-e6/id1166166909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fvoid-e4-b8-ad-e6-96-87-e6-94-be-e7-a9-ba-e5-86-a5-e6%2Fid1166166909&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=7e65fba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/void-e4-b8-ad-e6-96-87-e6-94-be-e7-a9-ba-e5-86-a5-e6/id1166166909</a><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，感謝。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭成功後，如有巴絲是讀社工、心理、輔導、治療師，請為有盡要嘅人進行輔導。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f29779de9fd37e66a180d15e649380d541d5e1d","tid":1222320,"uid":171684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"呢幾日成日行行下聽歌諗起就係街到喊 食lunch係快餐店睇啲消息睇到喊 自己放工番屋企一個人諗諗下覺得好嬲好唔憤氣 點解當日我地見證過每一個香港人既善良 要比個狗閪政府破壞 每次諗到呢到都會好嬲 喊到喘氣"},{"pid":"ba8ad382de61a4ee7adbafeea9157f891a39c128","tid":1222320,"uid":59664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"第2日返工個反差大到唔知點去適應，唔講以為去左異世界<br />\n覺又訓唔好，成個人無晒精神"},{"pid":"53cae00037a8ecdeedf84551a959c27ff608270a","tid":1222320,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"其實頭痛係咩事，有冇人解答到，痛左三日"},{"pid":"514200f5ef3b2c3917a587fa6243d74f7beb3dd9","tid":1222320,"uid":194298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:32:26.000Z","msg":"心理創傷，小心處理，搵個信得過既人講出你感受，攬住佢喊一場，最緊要係你無做錯到任何野，記住人生路漫長，今日發生既事只會令你將來更有勇氣<br />\n<br />\nPS. 14年經歷過"},{"pid":"70142ce2e4540c77317721b4cc302ae487bce742","tid":1222320,"uid":137802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74c99878ea1385643ece7ccee121b97c171de5ea","tid":1222320,"uid":35632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"日日訓醒都頭痛 仲不斷追post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲瘋狂過中學雞果陣喪打機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab5f88f3ace552119cc54477800cba33af449db","tid":1222320,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c23de6170ff041d192f5887adb6513efa72c18","tid":1222320,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53cae00037a8ecdeedf84551a959c27ff608270a","tid":1222320,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"其實頭痛係咩事，有冇人解答到，痛左三日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"無力感會令人沮喪，頭痛<br />\n<br />\n如果嚴重試下暫時停止接觸所有媒體資訊，包括社交同新聞<br />\n<br />\n去睇場戲唱個k，唔好覺得自己咁做係欠左香港<br />\n因為你已經係半個病人，其他戰友會幫你出埋果分力<br />\nE段時間好好休息先，來日方長"},{"pid":"0fb6d5d0d386dcfb335d55b925385d3998f6a026","tid":1222320,"uid":175808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wknews.org/node/570?fbclid=IwAR3HxI_DLCcBkBeL2JWnyK5SL2LLJ8bnts5E-Cdw8a-GZ9IoVqFA7KnllMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwknews.org%2Fnode%2F570%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3HxI_DLCcBkBeL2JWnyK5SL2LLJ8bnts5E-Cdw8a-GZ9IoVqFA7KnllMA&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=db968aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://wknews.org/node/570?fbclid=IwAR3HxI_DLCcBkBeL2JWnyK5SL2LLJ8bnts5E-Cdw8a-GZ9IoVqFA7KnllMA</a><br />\n<br />\n7%受胡椒噴霧噴中的人的角膜磨損<br />\n四分一吸入催淚氣的人出現感冒徵狀及感到疲倦<br />\n四分一女性在吸入催淚氣過後經期變得不規則<br />\n催淚彈會令所有心肺疾病惡化"},{"pid":"1cbcb712abae0ac323ca57e3d78527d5214c2536","tid":1222320,"uid":73033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"聽下班基督徒唱詩歌，好有舒緩作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae11ef913b6c9b2fa525d4fb55c323147ac624c","tid":1222320,"uid":47776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"69 晚 612通頂完到第二朝都唔覺<br />\n但依兩日黎料啦<br />\n好攰同好似頭間中暈暈地好似有少少發燒要請病假去睇睇醫生先<br />\n可能成個禮拜都精神緊張依家有少少放鬆就好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e2228abf8b47d34fc7a0297304641a3c462885","tid":1222320,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n好好休息下<br />\n情緒要釋放，唔好壓抑"},{"pid":"ec8cc30435443fa6c95ab5d7ad8d82f34607ca24","tid":1222320,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"你經歷過咁大型事件有咁嘅情緒同生理反應係正常 你可以試下同人講下感受或上嚟連登講 如果你想一啲情緒輔導可以搵紅十字會熱線 <br />\n但如果過了一至兩星期仍出現如失眠 驚恐 冇胃口 影響日常生活 可以搵臨床心理學家或精神科醫生查詢"},{"pid":"528ed2024121075bcc6c136279bb8000eb512e31","tid":1222320,"uid":187378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6BGLDP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BGLDP3.png&h=d00ef041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc37c087b4abd142d93404e3ad8d572d2960a0cd","tid":1222320,"uid":64743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:44:34.000Z","msg":"做乜都冇心機<br />\n睇下啲片<br />\n啲眼淚自己留出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}